cs.MA, cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the impact of social networks on multi-agent recommender systems, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). It also involves social networks (cs.SOC) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with recommending items to users. The paper also discusses network structures and parameters (cs.DS) and the impact of communication on the system (cs.SI).
